The paper deals with linear and bilinear inference problems, which are related to signal processing and machine learning. The use of belief propagation and the replica method suggests that the paper is likely to be categorized under information theory (cs.IT), machine learning (cs.LG), signal processing (cs.SP), multimedia (cs.MM), or social and information networks (cs.SI).
